description:
Fleetwood Mac-Fleetwood Mac (Deluxe 3-CD)FLAC ak 

In November 2017 the band announced a deluxe reissue of their 1975 self-titled album. The reissue features a remastered version of the original album along with unreleased outtakes, alternate versions and live versions. 


STYLE: Blues Rock, Rock
